- Don't move.

00:16:03.280 --> 00:16:04.359
Stay still.

00:16:06.239 --> 00:16:07.080
What is this for?

00:16:07.519 --> 00:16:09.519
I was worried you'd do something stupid.

00:16:09.680 --> 00:16:11.639
You pulled it so hard.

00:16:12.800 --> 00:16:14.920
It's cutting off my circulation.
Don't whine.

00:16:18.440 --> 00:16:19.680
Are you worried about me?

00:16:21.280 --> 00:16:22.800
Well, do you even need to ask?

00:16:23.759 --> 00:16:24.680
You think I'm crazy?

00:16:26.440 --> 00:16:27.359
Xu Dacheng,

00:16:28.400 --> 00:16:30.639
can't you ever just talk nicely?

00:16:41.479 --> 00:16:42.119
Zhidong?

00:16:43.359 --> 00:16:44.080
Zhidong?

00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:45.440
What are you doing here?

00:16:47.320 --> 00:16:48.160
What are you doing?

00:16:48.160 --> 00:16:48.800
Mom.

00:16:48.800 --> 00:16:49.560
What's wrong?

00:16:52.680 --> 00:16:53.200
Nothing.

00:16:53.210 --> 00:16:54.780
I was worried you'd do something stupid.

00:16:54.800 --> 00:16:57.080
Dad and I have to watch you together.

00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:02.800
Alright now.

00:17:03.759 --> 00:17:04.920
Go back to your room.

00:17:05.080 --> 00:17:06.359
Sleep in your room.

00:17:06.359 --> 00:17:07.680
It's okay, I'm not tired.

00:17:08.160 --> 00:17:09.119
Just go to bed.

00:17:09.119 --> 00:17:10.200
I'm really not tired.

00:17:11.280 --> 00:17:12.960
Alright, honey.

00:17:13.599 --> 00:17:14.559
I'm okay now.

00:17:14.759 --> 00:17:16.039
I've thought it through.

00:17:17.799 --> 00:17:19.640
I have to live.

00:17:20.680 --> 00:17:22.680
I have to live well
and find your second sister.

00:17:23.279 --> 00:17:24.600
Just for my second sister?

00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:27.319
And you guys too, of course.

00:17:27.319 --> 00:17:28.759
I have to stay alive and live well.

00:17:29.200 --> 00:17:30.559
If I died,

00:17:32.519 --> 00:17:34.479
your dad would just find another wife.

00:17:34.660 --> 00:17:36.759
Men in their fifties and
sixties can still have kids.

00:17:36.759 --> 00:17:38.759
And now the three-child
policy's open anyway.

00:17:39.039 --> 00:17:42.440
Why are you spouting nonsense
early in the morning?

00:17:42.440 --> 00:17:43.640
Tell me I'm wrong.

00:17:43.640 --> 00:17:44.840
Of course you're wrong.

00:17:45.200 --> 00:17:47.559
It's not just fifties or sixties,

00:17:47.960 --> 00:17:49.960
men can still have kids at eighty.

00:17:51.920 --> 00:17:53.200
Proud of it, huh?

00:17:53.600 --> 00:17:54.799
Aren't you tired?

00:17:56.360 --> 00:17:57.600
Alright, go to bed.

00:17:57.600 --> 00:17:59.640
- Where are you going?
- I'm going to make breakfast.

00:17:59.640 --> 00:18:00.960
Go back to bed.

00:18:00.960 --> 00:18:01.840
I'm coming with you.

00:18:01.960 --> 00:18:03.160
- Come on.
- Let's go together.

00:18:03.160 --> 00:18:03.680
Come on.

00:18:05.100 --> 00:18:07.740
(Nanzhou Elementary School)

00:18:22.680 --> 00:18:23.360
Lu Bing,

00:18:23.680 --> 00:18:24.880
a little red flower for you.

00:18:29.279 --> 00:18:30.440
What are you up to this time?

00:18:30.519 --> 00:18:31.680
And a tiny snake.

00:18:32.079 --> 00:18:33.960
Lu Bing, you're scaring it.

00:18:33.960 --> 00:18:35.120
It's scaring me!

00:18:35.120 --> 00:18:35.960
Get it away from me!

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:36.600
Try to touch it.

00:18:36.600 --> 00:18:37.840
Shen Minghui, stay away from me!

00:18:37.840 --> 00:18:38.450
It doesn't bite.

00:18:38.450 --> 00:18:39.440
I'm warning you, go away!

00:18:39.450 --> 00:18:40.060
It's obedient.

00:18:41.200 --> 00:18:42.600
Are you okay?

00:18:44.360 --> 00:18:45.319
Just you wait!

00:18:46.239 --> 00:18:47.920
She's mad.

00:18:59.440 --> 00:19:00.319
Shen Minghui!

00:19:23.880 --> 00:19:24.559
Honey,

00:19:24.960 --> 00:19:26.960
you know what's special about chives?

00:19:27.600 --> 00:19:29.079
What's so special about chives?

00:19:29.440 --> 00:19:30.519
Don't you get it?

00:19:30.799 --> 00:19:32.039
With you, I'm stir-fried!

00:19:35.440 --> 00:19:36.559
I saw it online.

00:19:39.759 --> 00:19:40.640
What time is it now?

00:19:43.440 --> 00:19:44.519
It's five twenty.

00:19:44.519 --> 00:19:45.760
You know what that means, right?

00:19:46.200 --> 00:19:47.519
From now on, I'm going to ask you

00:19:47.519 --> 00:19:48.680
at this time every day.

00:19:49.360 --> 00:19:50.640
Feng Jianqi,

00:19:51.319 --> 00:19:52.640
you're so gross.

00:19:53.279 --> 00:19:54.479
"Five twenty," my foot.

00:19:55.039 --> 00:19:57.120
You're a total idiot.

00:19:57.120 --> 00:19:58.920
Want me to give you another beating?

00:19:59.039 --> 00:20:00.559
See? I didn't even do anything to him.

00:20:00.820 --> 00:20:01.559
Just bear with it.

00:20:01.559 --> 00:20:02.479
Where's my soda?

00:20:03.840 --> 00:20:04.920
I gave it to Jianqi.

00:20:05.680 --> 00:20:06.559
Feng Jianqi!

00:20:07.200 --> 00:20:08.540
Who said you could drink my Coke?

00:20:08.560 --> 00:20:09.880
What's the big deal? I bought it.

00:20:09.880 --> 00:20:11.279
Why shouldn't Jianqi have some?

00:20:11.280 --> 00:20:12.850
There's a whole case of it right there.

00:20:13.120 --> 00:20:15.079
That's not the same! Mine was chilled!

00:20:15.750 --> 00:20:17.519
Mingzhu, why are you
always taking his side?

00:20:17.519 --> 00:20:18.960
Go upstairs and do your homework.

00:20:19.719 --> 00:20:20.759
Leave me alone!

00:20:22.260 --> 00:20:23.840
He's always looking for a fight with me.

00:20:24.200 --> 00:20:25.640
Just be the bigger person.

00:20:28.079 --> 00:20:28.719
Honey,

00:20:30.160 --> 00:20:32.039
Do you know what chopsticks symbolize?

00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:33.759
Chopsticks have a meaning too?

00:20:35.160 --> 00:20:36.510
What does one chopstick represent?

00:20:37.559 --> 00:20:38.239
Being single?

00:20:38.680 --> 00:20:39.440
And two?

00:20:42.160 --> 00:20:42.960
No idea.

00:20:43.160 --> 00:20:44.719
A perfect pair, just like you and me.

00:20:44.719 --> 00:20:46.319
Shen Minghui! Shen Minghui, come out!

00:20:46.600 --> 00:20:47.279
Where is he?

00:20:49.560 --> 00:20:50.479
Who are you looking for?

00:20:50.479 --> 00:20:51.479
What do you want?

00:20:53.239 --> 00:20:54.079
What do you want?

00:20:54.079 --> 00:20:55.160
Who are you looking for?

00:20:57.050 --> 00:20:58.600
Bully Lu Bing again, and I'll kill you!

00:20:58.600 --> 00:20:59.799
Why did you hit him?

00:21:00.680 --> 00:21:01.880
Are you okay, Jianqi?

00:21:02.640 --> 00:21:03.279
Jianqi?

00:21:03.380 --> 00:21:04.559
I thought it was Shen Minghui?

00:21:04.759 --> 00:21:05.279
Yes.

00:21:05.279 --> 00:21:05.759
Dude,

00:21:05.759 --> 00:21:06.880
did you hit the wrong person?

00:21:15.200 --> 00:21:16.120
Keep the bowls steady.

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:18.120
Wipe that smirk off your face.

00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:19.880
Want me to punish you more?

00:21:21.479 --> 00:21:22.719
Why are you giving him water?

00:21:22.999 --> 00:21:24.239
He's thirsty!

00:21:24.340 --> 00:21:25.920
What's the point of the punishment then?

00:21:26.799 --> 00:21:29.039
But we can't let him get dehydrated!

00:21:29.680 --> 00:21:30.759
Where are you going?

00:21:30.970 --> 00:21:32.840
The Qiao family ordered
ten jin of pork chops.

00:21:32.840 --> 00:21:33.799
I'm delivering them.

00:21:33.799 --> 00:21:34.479
You should stay.

00:21:34.479 --> 00:21:35.319
Don't you move.

00:21:35.319 --> 00:21:35.960
No, I mean,

00:21:35.960 --> 00:21:37.360
I'll go instead. They had a new baby.

00:21:37.360 --> 00:21:39.039
I haven't given them the red envelope.

00:21:39.799 --> 00:21:41.319
Mom, I'll go with you.

00:21:42.120 --> 00:21:42.759
Sure.

00:21:42.759 --> 00:21:43.880
I'll go with Mom.

00:21:43.880 --> 00:21:44.360
Okay.

00:21:44.360 --> 00:21:46.039
Jianqi, I'm going out with Mom.

00:21:46.039 --> 00:21:47.200
I'll be back soon.

00:21:47.880 --> 00:21:48.600
Got it!

00:21:48.880 --> 00:21:49.239
Hey,

00:21:49.239 --> 00:21:50.160
tuck your legs in.

00:21:50.519 --> 00:21:51.680
Closer.

00:21:52.880 --> 00:21:53.999
Hold it steady, steady now.

00:21:56.519 --> 00:21:57.440
All you do

00:21:58.759 --> 00:21:59.880
is causing trouble.

00:22:01.039 --> 00:22:01.799
Don't move.

00:22:02.999 --> 00:22:03.920
I'm watching you.

00:22:39.640 --> 00:22:41.039
Landlady,

00:22:41.440 --> 00:22:44.920
why is there no water?

00:22:48.079 --> 00:22:48.759
Minghui?

00:22:50.160 --> 00:22:50.840
Minghui?

00:22:52.440 --> 00:22:53.279
Are you there?

00:22:53.920 --> 00:22:54.719
What is it, Jianqi?

00:22:54.719 --> 00:22:56.319
I'm out of hot water.

00:22:56.319 --> 00:22:57.600
Can you take a look for me?

00:22:57.600 --> 00:22:58.759
Out of hot water?

00:22:59.559 --> 00:23:00.600
Let me see.

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:03.559
Jianqi,

00:23:04.880 --> 00:23:06.719
you took a beating for me today.

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:07.999
That's real loyalty.

00:23:09.279 --> 00:23:10.640
How about I give you a present?

00:23:12.840 --> 00:23:15.239
I'm counting on you, Little Hui.

00:23:17.279 --> 00:23:18.600
Avenge me.

00:23:18.999 --> 00:23:19.840
You got this.

00:23:20.279 --> 00:23:20.920
Go.

00:23:21.600 --> 00:23:22.920
Here's the hot water, Jianqi!

00:23:27.120 --> 00:23:29.319
No! Go away!

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:32.400
There's a snake in here!

00:23:32.400 --> 00:23:33.039
Minghui!

00:23:33.479 --> 00:23:34.120
Minghui!

00:23:36.039 --> 00:23:36.680
Minghui!

00:23:36.840 --> 00:23:38.239
Open the door! I'm scared of snakes!

00:23:38.239 --> 00:23:38.960
Minghui!

00:23:40.559 --> 00:23:41.440
Open the door!

