even if she sees it.

00:24:07.519 --> 00:24:09.079
But if her life has been hard,

00:24:09.759 --> 00:24:11.759
she'd definitely come

00:24:11.760 --> 00:24:12.640
to confront my parents.

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:15.200
She'd demand to know
why they gave her away.

00:24:15.200 --> 00:24:16.960
Should we still post it then?
I can delete it.

00:24:16.960 --> 00:24:17.840
No, don't delete it.

00:24:17.840 --> 00:24:19.360
I was just thinking out loud.

00:24:21.020 --> 00:24:22.920
Even if finding her
brings nothing but trouble,

00:24:23.440 --> 00:24:25.120
it's trouble our family deserves.

00:24:27.559 --> 00:24:29.799
Let's sleep. We have
a lot to do tomorrow.

00:24:30.039 --> 00:24:31.239
You're pregnant.

00:24:31.239 --> 00:24:33.039
You should really cut
back on your workload.

00:24:34.200 --> 00:24:35.600
Thank you for your concern, Hao.

00:24:35.600 --> 00:24:37.079
Now, be a dear and turn off the light.

00:24:44.799 --> 00:24:45.479
Honey,

00:24:46.239 --> 00:24:48.759
do you want a boy or a girl?

00:24:49.640 --> 00:24:51.440
I want a promotion and a raise.

00:24:52.220 --> 00:24:54.460
(Teacher's Office)

