This is Shen Minghui's
midterm exam paper.

00:24:57.719 --> 00:24:58.559
Take a look.

00:25:06.600 --> 00:25:08.200
His luck is just terrible.

00:25:08.260 --> 00:25:10.950
Even just picking C all the way
should have gotten him a few points.

00:25:13.120 --> 00:25:15.799
Tell me, was Shen Minghui adopted?

