If this is

00:25:23.479 --> 00:25:24.460
how your family

00:25:24.470 --> 00:25:26.759
treat his education,
then we have nothing more to discuss.

00:25:26.759 --> 00:25:28.039
No, Mr. Sun, I didn't mean that.

