He's been in high school for five years.

00:25:31.600 --> 00:25:33.239
He's been a senior for nearly three.

00:25:33.360 --> 00:25:35.079
The curriculum is exactly the same,

00:25:35.440 --> 00:25:37.840
but his grades aren't getting better,

00:25:37.840 --> 00:25:38.999
they're getting worse.

00:25:39.079 --> 00:25:39.759
Why?

00:25:41.360 --> 00:25:43.880
He just hasn't been in the right
headspace for studying lately.

00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:44.960
That's putting it mildly.

00:25:45.450 --> 00:25:46.960
He's not "out of the right headspace,"

00:25:47.479 --> 00:25:49.079
he has no headspace for it at all.

00:25:51.400 --> 00:25:52.079
Of course,

00:25:52.519 --> 00:25:54.680
he's very active in other areas.

00:25:55.440 --> 00:25:56.479
What other areas?

00:25:59.120 --> 00:26:00.759
He brought a snake to school

00:26:00.920 --> 00:26:02.400
and nearly scared Lu Bing to death.

00:26:02.680 --> 00:26:03.759
Do you know who Lu Bing is?

00:26:03.759 --> 00:26:05.759
She's our top student

00:26:05.799 --> 00:26:07.960
She got into a top-tier
university last year

00:26:07.960 --> 00:26:08.759
but didn't go.

00:26:08.760 --> 00:26:09.880
She's repeating her final year

00:26:09.880 --> 00:26:12.050
specifically to aim for
Tsinghua or Peking University.

00:26:13.039 --> 00:26:14.960
Wow, that's quite the gap between them.

00:26:16.200 --> 00:26:17.759
But don't worry, Mr. Sun,

00:26:17.999 --> 00:26:19.960
the situation with Lu Bing
has been resolved.

00:26:20.799 --> 00:26:21.600
Resolved? How?

00:26:22.079 --> 00:26:24.279
Lu Bing's brother came
over with some guys

00:26:24.840 --> 00:26:26.600
and beat up Minghui's brother-in-law.

00:26:26.850 --> 00:26:28.239
Even though they got the wrong guy,

00:26:28.239 --> 00:26:29.920
their family got it out of their system.

00:26:33.560 --> 00:26:34.560
Good that it's resolved.

00:26:35.640 --> 00:26:36.680
Anyway, here's the thing,

00:26:36.999 --> 00:26:39.360
we need to fix Minghui's

00:26:39.479 --> 00:26:41.160
academic problem immediately.

00:26:42.279 --> 00:26:44.279
He's a bright kid.

00:26:44.279 --> 00:26:45.239
Yes, he is.

00:26:45.240 --> 00:26:47.220
But he can't stay stuck
in his senior year forever.

00:26:47.239 --> 00:26:48.160
You're right.

00:26:48.519 --> 00:26:49.360
Let's work together,

00:26:49.960 --> 00:26:51.719
the school and your family,

00:26:51.999 --> 00:26:53.840
to help him make some real progress.

00:26:54.079 --> 00:26:55.160
Let's push hard this year

00:26:55.160 --> 00:26:56.360
and get his grades up.

00:26:56.360 --> 00:26:57.440
Got it. We'll push him.

00:27:07.239 --> 00:27:08.200
Mom and Dad.

00:27:08.799 --> 00:27:09.719
I'm home.

00:27:10.559 --> 00:27:11.400
You're home.

00:27:12.559 --> 00:27:13.319
How did it go?

00:27:14.640 --> 00:27:15.960
What did the school say?

00:27:15.960 --> 00:27:17.200
Let me have some water first.

00:27:20.200 --> 00:27:20.880
Easy there.

00:27:20.880 --> 00:27:21.640
How did it go?

00:27:23.479 --> 00:27:24.600
His teacher said a lot,

00:27:24.799 --> 00:27:25.880
but to sum it up,

00:27:26.410 --> 00:27:29.160
Nanzhou High School just wants to
get Minghui out as soon as possible.

00:27:29.759 --> 00:27:30.759
Out? To where?

00:27:30.759 --> 00:27:32.200
To college, of course.

00:27:32.440 --> 00:27:34.360
They've had enough of him.

00:27:34.360 --> 00:27:35.279
Oh, stop joking.

00:27:35.279 --> 00:27:36.120
College?

00:27:36.160 --> 00:27:37.680
You think you can
just send him there?

00:27:37.680 --> 00:27:39.120
Your family owns
the university now?

00:27:39.130 --> 00:27:40.120
You have to pass the exams to get in!

00:27:40.120 --> 00:27:41.920
You think I'm talking
about direct admission?

00:27:41.930 --> 00:27:43.350
The teachers are desperate.

00:27:43.350 --> 00:27:45.279
They said as long as
Minghui's willing to study,

00:27:45.279 --> 00:27:46.719
