Just look at the family
you've married into!

00:42:10.559 --> 00:42:12.320
What kind of people are they?

00:42:12.320 --> 00:42:12.960
Mom,

00:42:13.440 --> 00:42:15.079
I'll have a serious talk with Minghui.

00:42:16.079 --> 00:42:17.720
Go ahead, talk all you want.

00:42:20.840 --> 00:42:21.519
Mom,

00:42:22.199 --> 00:42:24.360
I don't care that you took the car back.

00:42:24.800 --> 00:42:26.360
I can bike to work.

00:42:27.320 --> 00:42:28.880
But I'm married to Mingzhu now,

00:42:28.880 --> 00:42:29.999
and she's pregnant.

00:42:31.159 --> 00:42:32.280
To be perfectly honest,

00:42:32.800 --> 00:42:33.920
if you can't accept her,

00:42:34.119 --> 00:42:35.240
then I'm never coming home.

00:42:35.440 --> 00:42:36.559
Suit yourself!

00:42:55.100 --> 00:42:56.950
The world is noisy

00:42:57.550 --> 00:42:59.930
Turning around,
it's already a distant view

00:43:01.350 --> 00:43:03.230
Once I didnt know what to do

00:43:03.230 --> 00:43:05.310
What to hold quietly

00:43:05.310 --> 00:43:08.260
Like a silent care

00:43:10.120 --> 00:43:12.530
Seasons pass by

00:43:12.530 --> 00:43:15.390
Time ticks away

00:43:15.880 --> 00:43:17.790
Seems like I understand a little

00:43:17.790 --> 00:43:19.570
And also let go of some things

00:43:19.570 --> 00:43:24.290
All the bittersweet flavors
are the essence of youth

00:43:24.290 --> 00:43:27.780
A long letter is written down

00:43:27.930 --> 00:43:31.410
Gently spreading love

00:43:31.610 --> 00:43:35.600
To all the forks in fate

00:43:35.600 --> 00:43:41.230
Loving all the moments
that deserve to be loved